import React from 'react'; function ReturnDetails(props) { const { localPhoneDetails } = props var rootStyle = { background: "rgba(255, 255, 242, .9)", color: '#AC3B61', overflow: 'hidden', width: '400px', fontFamily: 'Overpass,sans-serif', textAlign: 'left', alignItems: 'left' } return (
{localPhoneDetails ? localPhoneDetails.map((localPhoneDetail) => ( console.log("inside code: "), console.log(localPhoneDetail.result),

Number: {localPhoneDetail.result.Formatted}

Country name: {localPhoneDetail.result.Country}

Location: {localPhoneDetail.result.location}

Carrier: {localPhoneDetail.result["Line Provider"]}

Line type: {localPhoneDetail.result["Line Type"]}

)) : console.log('no map')}
) } export default ReturnDetails
